      <title>加密银行 Sygnum 融资 5800 万美元，跻身独角兽行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/crypto-bank-sygnum-hits-unicorn-status-with-58-million-raise</link>
